ompletion of the tasks. Totally useless. We need to come out with a new mindset, a new set of values and rules for successful <strong>corporate project management.</strong>\r\n\r\nIf any <strong>project manager</strong>, they should focus with the coordination of setting up dev, qa, staging and production environment. They should focus on merging project and release of project\r\n\r\n<strong>Jira </strong>is not necessarily the solution to everything. It is supposed to help within a project not define and guide the project. Yes the Epic and Stories concept are goods but they are just helpers.\r\n\r\nThe main difficulties in all corporate infrastructure or companies transitioning to corporate structure is the removal of the sense of the  <strong>individual\'s ownership.</strong>\r\n\r\nThe fordism is possible only when the process is fully master or when producing the exact same project all the time, to be applicable here few elements would need to be take into account\r\n- first\r\n- second\r\n\r\nThe importance to have a dedicated <strong>Information Architect</strong> in your company.  Someone focusing on designing and guiding the growing of the software infrastructure ineluctable\r\n\r\nThe use of Sequence diagram, UML is severly lacking. It is also time consuming for a developer since the sketch of this drawing need to be revsitied several times until completion\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Post Mortem Project timeline went wrong','','draft','closed','open','','','','','2018-08-07 23:44:17','2018-08-07 23:44:17','',0,'http://david.raleche.com/?p=53',0,'post','',0),(58,1,'2018-08-07 18:30:16','2018-08-07 18:30:16','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>4Over, Los Angeles - Technical Lead PHP</strong>\r\nSept 2017 - present\r\nAutomation of the manual direct mailing system. PHP Automated Restful API software(symfony) replacing a team of 10 people from the online order request to the electronic request submission to USPS. Heavy third party integration (USPS Postal One / Satori Ar